<section class="bg-neutral grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 border-b-2 border-primary">
  <div class="pillar reveal d1 px-6 sm:px-12 py-8 sm:py-10 text-center sm:border-r border-white/[0.08]">
    <h2 class="text-[1.1875rem] font-black text-primary mb-[0.625rem]">Honest scope.</h2>
    <p class="text-xs text-white/45 leading-[1.7]">
      I'll tell you upfront what I can do and what I can't. If it's something
      I need to figure out, that's on my dime — not yours.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="pillar reveal d2 px-6 sm:px-12 py-8 sm:py-10 text-center sm:border-r border-white/[0.08]">
    <h2 class="text-[1.1875rem] font-black text-secondary mb-[0.625rem]">Real timelines.</h2>
    <p class="text-xs text-white/45 leading-[1.7]">
      I give you a real finish date and keep you in the loop if anything
      changes. No phantom deadlines.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="pillar reveal d3 px-6 sm:px-12 py-8 sm:py-10 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-[1.1875rem] font-black text-accent mb-[0.625rem]">No surprises.</h2>
    <p class="text-xs text-white/45 leading-[1.7]">
      The price in the proposal is the price you pay. If something changes,
      we talk about it before any extra work starts.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
